div.p:
The first paragraph of the preamble is all right. Thereafter as follows: 

“The Republic of Bolivia by His Excellency Dr. Eduardo Diez de Medina,
                            Minister for Foreign Affairs, and His Excellency Dr. Enrique Finot,
                            President of the delegation of that country to the Peace Conference;

And the Republic of Paraguay by His Excellency Dr. Cecilio Baez, Minister
                            for Foreign Affairs; His Excellency General Jose Felix Estigarribia,
                            President of the delegation of that country to the Peace Conference, and
                            the delegates Their Excellencies Doctors Luis A. Riart and Efraim
                            Cardozo;

Present in Buenos Aires, et cetera”.
